panels.description: ⏱️ Follows date range. PRs Authored, Reviews Given, Balance, and Score per team member. Uses team_members table - run 'strands-metrics load-team' to configure.

targets.queryText:
WITH team_prs AS (
  SELECT 
    author,
    COUNT(*) as prs_authored
  FROM pull_requests
  WHERE merged_at IS NOT NULL
    AND author IN (SELECT username FROM team_members)
    AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(merged_at)) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
    AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(merged_at)) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
    AND repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')
  GROUP BY author
),
reviews AS (
  SELECT 
    author as reviewer,
    COUNT(DISTINCT repo || '-' || pr_number) as reviews_given
  FROM pr_reviews
  WHERE author IN (SELECT username FROM team_members)
    AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(submitted_at)) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
    AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(submitted_at)) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
    AND repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')
  GROUP BY author
)
SELECT 
  COALESCE(tp.author, r.reviewer) as "Team Member",
  COALESCE(tp.prs_authored, 0) as "PRs Authored",
  COALESCE(r.reviews_given, 0) as "Reviews Given",
  COALESCE(r.reviews_given, 0) - COALESCE(tp.prs_authored, 0) as "Balance",
  COALESCE(tp.prs_authored, 0) * 2 + COALESCE(r.reviews_given, 0) as "Score"
FROM team_prs tp
FULL OUTER JOIN reviews r ON tp.author = r.reviewer
WHERE COALESCE(tp.prs_authored, 0) + COALESCE(r.reviews_given, 0) > 0
ORDER BY "Score" DESC

panels.title: 📊 Team Scorecard

panels.description: ⏱️ Follows date range. Git Gladiator = Most PRs. Relentless Reviewer = Most Reviews.

targets.queryText:
SELECT * FROM (
  SELECT '🏆 Git Gladiator' as "Category", author as "Leader", COUNT(*) as "Count"
  FROM pull_requests
  WHERE merged_at IS NOT NULL
    AND author IN (SELECT username FROM team_members)
    AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(merged_at)) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
    AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(merged_at)) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
    AND repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')
  GROUP BY author ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1
)
UNION ALL
SELECT * FROM (
  SELECT '🔍 Relentless Reviewer' as "Category", author as "Leader", COUNT(DISTINCT repo || '-' || pr_number) as "Count"
  FROM pr_reviews
  WHERE author IN (SELECT username FROM team_members)
    AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(submitted_at)) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
    AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(submitted_at)) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
    AND repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')
  GROUP BY author ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT repo || '-' || pr_number) DESC LIMIT 1
)

panels.title: 🏅 Category Leaders

panels.description: ⏱️ Follows date range. Weekly (reviews given - PRs authored). Positive = team reviewing more.

targets.queryText:
WITH weekly_stats AS (
  SELECT 
    strftime('%Y-%m-%d', date(merged_at, 'weekday 0', '-6 days')) as week_start,
    COUNT(*) as pr_count,
    0 as review_count
  FROM pull_requests
  WHERE merged_at IS NOT NULL
    AND author IN (SELECT username FROM team_members)
    AND repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')
  GROUP BY week_start
  
  UNION ALL
  
  SELECT 
    strftime('%Y-%m-%d', date(submitted_at, 'weekday 0', '-6 days')) as week_start,
    0 as pr_count,
    COUNT(DISTINCT repo || '-' || pr_number) as review_count
  FROM pr_reviews
  WHERE author IN (SELECT username FROM team_members)
    AND repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')
  GROUP BY week_start
)
SELECT 
  CAST(strftime('%s', week_start) as INTEGER) as time,
  'Review Balance' as metric,
  SUM(review_count) - SUM(pr_count) as value
FROM weekly_stats
WHERE CAST(strftime('%s', week_start) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', week_start) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
GROUP BY week_start
ORDER BY week_start
targets.rawQueryText:

  SELECT 
    strftime('%Y-%m-%d', date(merged_at, 'weekday 0', '-6 days')) as week_start,
    COUNT(*) as pr_count,
    0 as review_count
  FROM pull_requests
  WHERE merged_at IS NOT NULL
    AND author IN (SELECT username FROM team_members)
    AND repo IN (${repo:singlequote})
  GROUP BY week_start
  
  UNION ALL
  
  SELECT 
    strftime('%Y-%m-%d', date(submitted_at, 'weekday 0', '-6 days')) as week_start,
    0 as pr_count,
    COUNT(DISTINCT repo || '-' || pr_number) as review_count
  FROM pr_reviews
  WHERE author IN (SELECT username FROM team_members)
    AND repo IN (${repo:singlequote})
  GROUP BY week_start
)
SELECT 
  CAST(strftime('%s', week_start) as INTEGER) as time,
  'Review Balance' as metric,
  SUM(review_count) - SUM(pr_count) as value
FROM weekly_stats
WHERE CAST(strftime('%s', week_start) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', week_start) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
GROUP BY week_start
ORDER BY week_start

panels.title: 📈 Team Review Balance (Weekly)

panels.description: ⏱️ Follows date range. Pie chart of merged PRs by source: Team (from team_members table), Community, Dependabot. Run 'strands-metrics load-team' to configure.

targets.queryText:
SELECT 
  CASE 
    WHEN author IN (SELECT username FROM team_members) THEN 'Team'
    WHEN author LIKE '%[bot]%' OR author = 'dependabot' THEN 'Dependabot'
    ELSE 'Community'
  END as category,
  COUNT(*) as count
FROM pull_requests
WHERE merged_at IS NOT NULL
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(merged_at)) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(merged_at)) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
  AND repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')
GROUP BY category
targets.rawQueryText:

  CASE 
    WHEN author IN (SELECT username FROM team_members) THEN 'Team'

    ELSE 'Community'

  COUNT(*) as count
FROM pull_requests
WHERE merged_at IS NOT NULL
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(merged_at)) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(merged_at)) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
  AND repo IN (${repo:singlequote})
GROUP BY category
